---
# Panel dev overrides — consumed by /panel-setup → writes panel/.env.local
supabase_url: https://your-project.supabase.co
supabase_anon_key: your-anon-key
mcp_http_url: http://localhost:8000/mcp

# Feature flags
enable_echo_out_style: true
enable_filter_sweep_style: true

# Default set-building behaviour
default_template: peak_hour_60
default_crossfade_bars: 32
default_analysis_level: 3

# VM background jobs
vm_host: root@your-vm-host
vm_workers: 12
vm_sleep_sec: 600
---

# DJ Music Plugin — per-project settings

Copy this file to `.claude/dj-music.local.md` and customise. The copy
is gitignored — safe for tokens and host addresses.

See `docs/plugin-settings.md` for the field reference.
